page1.title: About Me
page1.content: Hi I am Prakash Natarajan 🙂 . I enjoy architecting software systems. 👨‍💻 . This website contains my notes from various sources I find interesting in internet. 📓 . I approach the problem for solving it by best possible method rather than inserting a specific technology for my clients. 🧰 . Please reach out to me at 📨 mail@prakashn.com if you need any assistance with your software needs. 💚 . Take care. 👋 .
